
		AVA - Discord Bot Documentation Repository
		===========================================

This is the documentation repository for Ava, a Discord bot integrated
with OpenClaw. It contains the legal and policy documents required for
operating the bot on the Discord platform.

WHAT IS THIS REPOSITORY?

  This repository hosts the official documentation for Ava, including:

    - Terms and Conditions
    - Privacy Policy

  These documents are published as GitHub Pages and are required by
  Discord and OpenClaw for bot verification and compliance.

PAGES

  Terms and Conditions:
    https://adarshba.github.io/Ava/terms.html

  Privacy Policy:
    https://adarshba.github.io/Ava/privacy.html

CONTACT

  For any questions regarding these documents, please open an issue in
  this repository or contact the bot owner through Discord.

LICENSE

  The documentation in this repository is provided as-is. All rights
  reserved by the repository owner.
